<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:vellum="http://commcarehq.org/xforms/vellum">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Quick</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/A80E364E-E361-4685-A0C8-AA3686E67305" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Quick">
					<question1 />
					<question2 />
					<question3 />
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/question1" type="xsd:int" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/question2" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/question3" type="xsd:string" />
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="question1-label">
						<value>question1</value>
					</text>
					<text id="question2-label">
						<value>question2</value>
					</text>
					<text id="question2-item1-label">
						<value>item1</value>
					</text>
					<text id="question2-item2-label">
						<value>item2</value>
					</text>
					<text id="question3-label">
						<value>question3</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<input ref="/data/question1">
			<label ref="jr:itext('question1-label')" />
		</input>
		<select1 ref="/data/question2">
			<label ref="jr:itext('question2-label')" />
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('question2-item1-label')" />
				<value>item1</value>
			</item>
			<item>
				<label ref="jr:itext('question2-item2-label')" />
				<value>item2</value>
			</item>
		</select1>
		<input ref="/data/question3">
			<label ref="jr:itext('question3-label')" />
		</input>
	</h:body>
</h:html>
_attachments.f7c3574b3386a9f830694159e3c8f6ce6f155b2a:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa">
    <h:head>
        <h:title>User Registration</h:title>
        <model>
            <instance>
                <user_registration xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://code.javarosa.org/user_registration" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="User Registration">
                    <username />
                    <password />
                    <confirmpass />
                </user_registration>
            </instance>
            <bind nodeset="/user_registration/username" type="xsd:string" />
            <bind nodeset="/user_registration/password" type="xsd:int" />
            <bind nodeset="/user_registration/confirmpass" type="xsd:int" constraint="/user_registration/password = ." />
            <itext>
                <translation lang="en" default="">
                    <text id="username-label">
                        <value>Username</value>
                    </text>
                    <text id="password-label">
                        <value>Password</value>
                    </text>
                    <text id="confirmpass-label">
                        <value>Please Confirm Password</value>
                    </text>
                </translation>
            </itext>
        </model>
    </h:head>
    <h:body>
        <input ref="/user_registration/username">
            <label ref="jr:itext('username-label')" />
        </input>
        <secret ref="/user_registration/password">
            <label ref="jr:itext('password-label')" />
        </secret>
        <secret ref="/user_registration/confirmpass">
            <label ref="jr:itext('confirmpass-label')" />
        </secret>
    </h:body>
</h:html>

_attachments.49f053f88168cf31abaad113ae138cae6245086a:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:vellum="http://commcarehq.org/xforms/vellum">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Repeat group</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/84A114F6-7F7F-4AE6-B82F-EFB25DA38A66" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Repeat group">
					<repeat jr:template="">
						<repeat_label />
						<number />
					</repeat>
					<three />
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/repeat" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/repeat/repeat_label" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/repeat/number" type="xsd:int" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/three" calculate="3" />
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="repeat-label">
						<value>repeat</value>
					</text>
					<text id="repeat_label-label">
						<value>I repeat myself</value>
					</text>
					<text id="number-label">
						<value>Some number</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<group>
			<label ref="jr:itext('repeat-label')" />
			<repeat nodeset="/data/repeat" jr:count="/data/three">
				<trigger ref="/data/repeat/repeat_label" appearance="minimal">
					<label ref="jr:itext('repeat_label-label')" />
				</trigger>
				<input ref="/data/repeat/number">
					<label ref="jr:itext('number-label')" />
				</input>
			</repeat>
		</group>
	</h:body>
</h:html>
